content: Ms. Marks,Thank you for reaching out to us here at Capital Metro regarding the mobile app issue you were experiencing. Please accept our apology for any inconvenience this may have caused.The issue should be resolved. Please check to see if you can see and access your passes.If you continue to have issues, please contact us here or the Go Line at 512-474-1200.Thank you,Sondra WilliamsContact Center SupervisorCapital Metro. Transportation Auth.512.474.1200customer.service@capmetro.org
